25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：在学习 Linux 后渗透、隧道与持久化机制的读者。\n阅读前提：具备基础 Shell、SSH 和 Linux 权限管理经验。\n核心收获：构建后渗透阶段的控制、隐蔽和维持访问思路。\n说明：示例仅适用于授权实验环境，生产系统请优先做检测与加固。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"当渗透测试人员成功获取目标系统的访问权限后，工作并没有结束。后渗透（Post-Exploitation）阶段的目标是维持访问、深入探索内网、收集敏感数据、并建立持久化后门。本文将系统地讲解反弹 Shell 的各种技术、Shell 升级方法、SSH 隧道搭建、持久化手段、痕迹清理等后渗透关键技术，这些都是渗透测试报告中需要覆盖的重要内容。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"反弹-shell-技术大全","children":["反弹 Shell 技术大全",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#反弹-shell-技术大全","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"反弹 Shell（Reverse Shell）是渗透测试中最基本的技术之一。目标机器主动连接攻击者的监听端口，绕过防火墙的入站限制。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"攻击端监听设置","children":["攻击端监听设置",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#攻击端监听设置","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"在发送任何反弹 Shell 之前，需要先在攻击机上设置监听："}],"\n","$L2d","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"bash-反弹-shell","children":["Bash 反弹 Shell",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#bash-反弹-shell","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2e","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"python-反弹-shell","children":["Python 反弹 Shell",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#python-反弹-shell","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2f","\n","$L30","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"netcat-反弹-shell","children":["Netcat 反弹 Shell",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#netcat-反弹-shell","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L31","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"php-反弹-shell","children":["PHP 反弹 Shell",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#php-反弹-shell","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L32","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"perl-反弹-shell","children":["Perl 反弹 Shell",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#perl-反弹-shell","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L33","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"ruby-反弹-shell","children":["Ruby 反弹 Shell",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#ruby-反弹-shell","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L34","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"其他反弹-shell","children":["其他反弹 Shell",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#其他反弹-shell","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L35","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"shell-升级技术","children":["Shell 升级技术",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#shell-升级技术","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"通过反弹 Shell 获得的通常是一个非交互式的简陋 Shell，无法使用 Tab 补全、方向键、Ctrl+C 等。需要进行 Shell 升级。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"python-pty-升级","children":["Python PTY 升级",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#python-pty-升级","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L36","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"使用-script-命令升级","children":["使用 script 命令升级",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#使用-script-命令升级","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L37","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"使用-socat-升级","children":["使用 socat 升级",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#使用-socat-升级","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L38","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"ssh-隧道技术","children":["SSH 隧道技术",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#ssh-隧道技术","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"SSH 隧道是后渗透中最重要的网络技术之一，可以用来访问内网资源、绕过防火墙、建立代理通道。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"本地端口转发local-port-forwarding","children":["本地端口转发（Local Port Forwarding）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#本地端口转发local-port-forwarding","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"将攻击机本地端口的流量转发到目标内网中的某个服务。"}],"\n","$L39","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"远程端口转发remote-port-forwarding","children":["远程端口转发（Remote Port Forwarding）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#远程端口转发remote-port-forwarding","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"将目标机器上的端口转发到攻击机，适用于目标机器无法被直接访问的场景。"}],"\n","$L3a","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"动态端口转发socks-代理","children":["动态端口转发（SOCKS 代理）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#动态端口转发socks-代理","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"创建一个 SOCKS 代理，可以访问目标内网的任意服务。"}],"\n","$L3b","\n","$L3c","\n","$L3d","\n","$L3e","\n","$L3f","\n","$L40","\n","$L41","\n","$L42","\n","$L43","\n","$L44","\n","$L45","\n","$L46","\n","$L47","\n","$L48","\n","$L49","\n","$L4a","\n","$L4b","\n","$L4c","\n","$L4d","\n","$L4e","\n","$L4f","\n","$L50","\n","$L51","\n","$L52","\n","$L53","\n","$L54","\n","$L55","\n","$L56","\n","$L57","\n","$L58","\n","$L59","\n","$L5a"]
