58:["$","ol",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"网络监控"}],"：部署 IDS/IPS 检测异常的出站连接和隧道流量"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"端口限制"}],"：使用防火墙严格限制出站连接，仅允许必要的端口和目标"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"SSH 加固"}],"：禁用 SSH 端口转发（",["$","code",null,{"children":"AllowTcpForwarding no"}],"），限制 SSH 密钥"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"文件完整性监控"}],"：使用 AIDE/OSSEC 监控关键系统文件（",["$","code",null,{"children":"/etc/passwd"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"children":"/etc/crontab"}],"、systemd 服务）"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"日志集中管理"}],"：将日志发送到远程日志服务器（如 ELK/Splunk），防止本地日志被篡改"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"进程监控"}],"：监控异常进程和网络连接，使用 EDR 工具检测恶意行为"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"定期审计"}],"：定期检查 authorized_keys、crontab、systemd 服务、SUID 文件"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"最小权限"}],"：限制用户的 sudo 权限和文件访问权限"]}],"\n"]}]
